title: Perilous Pursuit
content:
This is a keen 1 mod continuing the story of Goodbye Galaxy. Most of the graphics and levels were done be me, while commander spleen worked on the patching, sound affects, and other fixes. Have fun playing:

Commander Keen in "Goobye Galaxy!"
Episode VI: Perilous Pursuit

[url=http://jimsoft.spatang.com/keen/spleen/archive/pursuit.zip]jimsoft.spatang.com/keen/...ursuit.zip[/url]

-Ceilick-
